body.p: The County Administrative Board can provide you with funding for a project that fosters regional growth and development.

The purpose of the project funding is to strengthen local and regional competitiveness in all parts of the country. You can apply for project funding, if you and others have an idea that you want to implement in a project. The project should be something new, be outside the core activities and be well defined in time. The results of the project should be of benefit to others.
